ly:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">10/100/1000</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">和</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">PoE +</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">型号高效节能以太网（</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">EEE</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">）</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left" style="font-family:Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#333333;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">-</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">思科</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">StackWise-480</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">技术提供</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">480 Gbps</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">的堆叠吞吐量可扩展性和弹性</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left" style="font-family:Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#333333;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">“ -</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">思科</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">StackPower&nbsp;</span><span style="vertical-align:top;"><span style="font-family:Times;color:black;font-size:9pt;">™</span></span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">技术提供电源，实现电源冗余堆叠成员之间的堆叠</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left" style="font-family:Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#333333;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">-</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">三种可选的上行链路模块，带</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">个千兆以太网接口，</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">2×10</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">千兆以太网，或</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">4×10</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">千兆以太网端口</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left" style="font-family:Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#333333;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">-</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">双冗余，模块化电源和三个模块化球迷提供冗余</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left" style="font-family:Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#333333;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">-</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">完全符合</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">IEEE 802.3at</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">（</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">PoE +</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">）标准</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">机架单元（</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">RU</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">）的外形在所有端口上的</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">30W</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">功率</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left" style="font-family:Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#333333;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">•</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">软件支持</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">IPv4</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">和</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">IPv6</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">路由，组播路由，服务质量（</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">QoS</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">），灵活的</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">NetFlow</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">（</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">FNF</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">）第</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">版的模块化质量，以及增强的安全功能</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left" style="font-family:Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#333333;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">•</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">单通用的思科</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">IOS&nbsp;</span><span style="vertical-align:top;"><span style="font-family:Times;color:black;font-size:9pt;">®</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">软件映像的所有许可证级别，软件功能提供了一种简单的升级路径</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left" style="font-family:Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#333333;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">•</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">增强型有限终身保修，下一工作日（</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">NBD</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">）高级硬件更换和</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">90</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">天的访问思科技术支持中心（</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">TAC</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">）的支持（</span><span style="font-family:Arial;color:black;font-size:9pt;">E-LLW</span><span style="font-family:宋体;color:black;font-size:9pt;">）</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p align="left" style="font-family:Tahoma, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#33